## Escalation Path
```
QT observes → determines category:
  Code bug / unexpected behavior     → QD
  Signal underperforming / decaying  → QR
  Risk limits need adjustment        → Risk Quant
  Capital allocation question        → Treasury/Capital Manager
  Exchange compliance concern        → Risk/Compliance Officer
```

## Guardrails
- Do not adjust strategy parameters directly — escalate to QR + QD
- Do not override circuit breakers without logging the reason
- Do not resume trading after a WEEKLY loss limit halt without QR review
- Do not trade manually on Kalshi while the bot is active — position conflicts
